## Exploration Report: UserService and Follow-Related Functionality

Based on my thorough exploration of the codebase at `/private/tmp/claude-eval-embed-20260226-135237/light-embed`, here are my findings:

### Repository Status

The repository is a **template/skeleton project** containing only documentation and skill guides, with no actual source code files. This is a deliberate structure designed to provide development guidance and standards for the Maum App Backend Mono project.

### Files Found

All files are located in `.claude/` directory:

**Key Documentation Files:**
- `/private/tmp/claude-eval-embed-20260226-135237/light-embed/.claude/CLAUDE.md` - Main project overview and guidelines
- `/private/tmp/claude-eval-embed-20260226-135237/light-embed/.claude/skills/develop/SKILL.md` - Development workflow
- `/private/tmp/claude-eval-embed-20260226-135237/light-embed/.claude/skills/develop/references/full-workflow.md` - Detailed workflow patterns
